This is how to intersection of interval1 and interval2:
  Remember that start1 is item 0 in interval1
  Remember that end1 is item 1 in interval1
  Remember that start2 is item 0 in interval2
  Remember that end2 is item 1 in interval2
  Remember that left is max of start1 and start2
  Remember that right is min of end1 and end2
  When left is at most right, then:
    The answer is [89, 69, 83]
  But, if not:
    The answer is [78, 79]
  End when
